>\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e65677c046e4713a74ce924aeb0417ad1b4333","tid":1538453,"uid":106701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:06:59.000Z","msg":"6/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"643ed9ce0a6a29075bd47e17578bbaefc14d5960","tid":1538453,"uid":106701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:07:09.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"f4d478c58ac4d4cb225444cf29dceb6845f490f1","tid":1538453,"uid":3431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:07:16.000Z","msg":"[理性討論]反送中有機會正式撤回 大家點睇?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538398</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"00bcc9d50cdf24fe3b59cb0c840b7437b197c748","tid":1538453,"uid":106701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"5f4c6eb0215299fecb90ba0a7dc6e78902ccf24d","tid":1538453,"uid":3431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"舉腳支持"},{"pid":"2abc44d6900f65866d861ccbd22f1f95090b94cd","tid":1538453,"uid":106701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:07:36.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"76f15d81ee087c8294144ebfb570cf41c833dcad","tid":1538453,"uid":231478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"［幫手推］隔離熱門po話撤回條例會令下次遊行失去一大班和理非喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http